The,MapQuest,Open,Guidance,API,allows,developers,to,create,mobile,navigation,applications,Rather,than,simply,providing,the,geometry,of,a,route,and,narrative,directions,the,Guidance,API,shares,the,graph,and,nodes,of,the,streets,Developers,can,use,the,service,along,with,the,user,s,current,location,to,determine,what,street,a,user,is,passing,and,whether,the,user,needs,to,turn,The,MapQuest,Open,Guidance,API,is,built,on,OpenStreetMap,data,Like,other,open,MapQuest,services,this,one,is,made,available,free,of,charge,and,without,limits,The,RESTful,API,returns,either,XML,or,JSON